        <div class="slds-popover__body" id="dialog-body-id-263" data-aura-rendered-by="25:392;a"><h1 style="padding-bottom: 5px;" data-aura-rendered-by="26:392;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="27:392;a">Risks Tracked by the SCE</b></h1><p data-aura-rendered-by="37:1267;a"><u data-aura-rendered-by="38:1267;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="39:1267;a">Key Contact Change</b></u>: Additions or deletions of important contacts affiliated with the account.</p><p data-aura-rendered-by="43:1267;a"><u data-aura-rendered-by="44:1267;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="45:1267;a">C-Suite Executive Change</b></u>: Additions or deletions of any member of the C-Suite within the account (CEO, CFO, COO, etc.)</p><p data-aura-rendered-by="49:1267;a"><u data-aura-rendered-by="50:1267;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="51:1267;a">M&amp;A Activity</b></u>: Company is interested in acquiring or has acquired another organization or is at risk of being acquired or has been acquired by another company. Looking for significant activity, not routine.</p><p data-aura-rendered-by="55:1267;a"><u data-aura-rendered-by="56:1267;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="57:1267;a">Economic &amp; Financial Risk Activity</b></u>: The business or the industry the client is engaged in is in turmoil or layoffs due to financial pressure or significant stock price decline.</p><p data-aura-rendered-by="61:1267;a"><u data-aura-rendered-by="62:1267;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="63:1267;a">Exchange Risk Activity</b></u>: Non exchange clients have expressed interest or have taken action to evaluate an exchange for the coming year.</p><p data-aura-rendered-by="67:1267;a"><u data-aura-rendered-by="68:1267;a"><b data-aura-rendered-by="69:1267;a">Key Consultant Change</b></u>: The account has made a change in Consultant or Consulting Firm.</p>
